  • Property is offered "as is, where is".
  • We reserve the right to place bids on behalf of the seller up to the seller's reserve price. This provides buyers and sellers more flexibility to reach a mutually agreeable price. Bids placed on behalf of seller do not occur once the seller's reserve price has been met.
